</figure>
<p data-index="2498"><a class="blue" id="c22-fig-0020-a" href="c22.xhtml#c22-fig-0020" data-index="2499" data-section-index="32" data-section-idref="c22-fig-0020" data-target-data-index="2501"><b data-index="2500">Illustration 22.20</b></a> shows the entries that Selectro should have made and did make for recording depreciation expense and income taxes.</p>
