<td style=" vertical-align: top;" data-index="4375"><div class="left" data-index="4376">9,600<a id="c22-note-0201-a" href="c22.xhtml#c22-note-0201" data-index="4377" data-section-index="32" data-section-idref="c22-note-0201" data-target-data-index="4385">*</a></div></td>
