<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0273" data-index="5069"><span class="label" data-index="5070"><b data-index="5071">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is the beginning retained earnings balance at January 1, 2020, if Gordon prepares comparative financial statements starting in 2020?</p>
