<h4 data-index="5171"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="22-43" id="Page_22-43" data-index="5172"></span><span class="red" data-index="5173">Instructions</span></h4>
<p data-index="5174">Answer the following questions.</p>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0277" data-index="5175"><span class="label" data-index="5176"><b data-index="5177">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> If comparative income statements are prepared, what net income should Kenseth report in 2019 and 2020?</p>
