<h4 data-index="5700"><span class="red" data-index="5701">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0319" data-index="5702"><span class="label" data-index="5703"><b data-index="5704">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Assuming that the books have not been closed, what are the adjusting entries necessary at December 31, 2021? (Ignore income tax considerations.)</p>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0320" data-index="5705"><span class="label" data-index="5706"><b data-index="5707">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Assuming that the books have been closed, what are the adjusting entries necessary at December 31, 2021? (Ignore income tax considerations.)</p>
