<h4 data-index="5985"><span class="red" data-index="5986">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0327" data-index="5987"><span class="label" data-index="5988"><b data-index="5989">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What effect does the January 2, 2020, transaction have upon Aykroyd's accounting treatment for its investment in Martin?</p>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0328" data-index="5990"><span class="label" data-index="5991"><b data-index="5992">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Compute the carrying amount of the investment in Martin as of December 31, 2020 (prior to any fair value adjustment).</p>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0329" data-index="5993"><span class="label" data-index="5994"><b data-index="5995">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare the adjusting entry on December 31, 2020, applying the fair value method to Aykroyd's long-term investment in Martin Company securities.</p>
