<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0334" data-index="6353"><span class="label" data-index="6354"><b data-index="6355">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare the journal entries to record depreciation expense for 2020 and correct any errors made to date related to the information provided. (Ignore taxes.)</p>
<p class="latin1" id="c22-ex-0335" data-index="6356"><span class="label" data-index="6357"><b data-index="6358">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Show comparative net income for 2019 and 2020. Income before depreciation expense was $300,000 in 2020, and was $310,000 in 2019. (Ignore taxes.)</p>
