<li data-index="6541"><b data-index="6542">4.</b> Before 2020, Penn accounted for its income from long-term construction contracts on the completed-contract basis. Early in 2020, Penn changed to the percentage-of-completion basis for accounting purposes. It continues to use the completed-contract method for tax purposes. Income for 2020 has been recorded using the percentage-of-completion method. The following information is available.
